Ladies man if you've an old dvd player that doesn't play divx format these avi files won't play on your player, but if you're dvd player plays divx just burn the files to disc and enjoy, you can get up to six movies on one disc depending on the file sizes, (6, 700mb files).
If you haven't got a player that plays divx I suggest you buy one, you can pick them up for little or nothing these days.

It's not a matter of complexity. This film is a satire on man's feeble efforts to discover the God particle and unlock the secrets of existence and reality in the four dimensional spacetime observable to humans.

Kestral said "I knew why we're here the first time I dropped acid." Later he said "The reason why we're here, is to learn why we're here."

Typical acid head hallucinogen logic. Classic.
